<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20010124092200/http://library.thinkquest.org/2886/">Bizarre American Holidays</a> – a comprehensive compilation of special recognition given both to months and individual days. <i>Unfortunately, the origins of the commemorations aren't provided.</i></li>
